Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  吉井
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在  试兽召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,327)}{\fs14}〈Summon〉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察处分者·吉井明久的召唤兽有着特殊用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅能够触摸到实际物体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且利用他那经过数倍增幅的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我把世界地图拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮老师打杂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉井  把桌子搬到视听教室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉井  把球门收拾起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  为什么老是使唤我一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是观察处分者的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察处分者的召唤兽受到的疼痛也会反馈到使用者身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要进行小测验  给我好好复习迄今为止学过的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向你复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:55.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}（*日文中  复习与复仇的发音相同）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:00:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨~蛋
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//-------------------OPJP--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:11.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放っといて育つものなんだ　なんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:12.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one more chance, one more chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:14.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one more chance, one more chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:16.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出会いましては簡単すぎるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:32.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初に決めた答えはひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:35.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ときめきました合格しますか?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋も勝負もあわてない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:40.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,コツコツコツと徹夜に溜息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:43.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のなかに天才dreamer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うことみな叶えばいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:48.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人の世界はきにしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect-area complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対ここで待ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:02:00.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect-area　望む声が聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:01.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah! EAR EAR!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?　とまらないすれちがい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:07.25,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私が相談相手なら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「友達かい?」「友達です。」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しき0点だね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:15.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!　やりなおしかきなおし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本気で　one more chance please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:21.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまより素敵な未来があるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:28.00,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまより素敵に　my life, my life, my life!!
