Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:24.35,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,120)}{\fs11}例句……以拳击拳  威力抵消
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:24.35,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(324,64)}{\fs11}老师点评
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:24.35,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(302,71)}{\fs11}很可惜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:24.35,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(281,133)}{\fs11}虽然它也有「so u sa tsu」的读法
